channel.title: Coder Looking To Help---100% FREE
channel.description:
Hi, I'm a coder who is currently working on a new server "LeScape Pk", as my name suggests. I am a good coder I believe, but there is still more I would like to know. I will code for someones server, the more things you demand, I look them up, figure out how to do it, and then I have another thing I can add to my new server before i decide to release it. I will code for you 100% FREE, all I ask for is administrator position on your server, and I will try my absolute best to find and (add\edit) anything you want into your server.
I own a server currently online called "Le Hawtz Pk Server", if you want to check that server out to see what I've done, it is a hamachi server. The Information for logging on is below

I just want people to be able to see what I have done and am able to do. My M.S.N. account is imthat_onedude@hotmail.com and I can be E-Mailed at z_noel@sbcglobal.net
